high_descs: Turn left and head to the entrance to the other room then turn right and face the side of the dresser
Pick up the gold statue
turn around then head across the room to your left, walk to the right hand black stand then turn right and walk to the window then turn left and face the tall floor lamp
Turn on the floor lamp
anns.task_desc: Examine a statue under a tall lamp

high_descs: Walk to the statue on the dresser against the wall on your left.
Pick up the statue from the dresser.
Turn around, walk into the room on the left and head to the floor lamp in the top right corner of the room.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a statue by the light of a floor lamp.

high_descs: Move forward, turn left, go into the other room, turn right and go to the side of the black table.
Pick up the statue on the table.
Bring the statue back into the first room, head to the tall lamp in the corner.
Turn on the tall lamp in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Examine the statue by the light of the lamp in the corner.

high_descs: Go forward and slightly left to the dresser on the left side of the partial wall.
Pick up the trophy.
Turn right and go forward, then turn right to go to the corner of the room with the lamp in it.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Look at a trophy illuminated by a lamp.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the dark cabinet across from the sofa
Pick up the trophy from the cabinet
Turn around and walk over to the tall floor lamp in the corner by the chair
Turn on the lamp
anns.task_desc: Examine the trophy by the light of the floor lamp

high_descs: Walk towards the chair, enter the room to the left, turn right to face the trophy.
Pick up the trophy from the table.
Turn around, walk towards the white pillar, make a left towards the tall lamp across the room.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a trophy by the light of a tall lamp.
